 locales uninhabitable.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In the coming years, the CHG will broaden its focus to include more nations, as well as longer time horizons.<\\/p>\\r\\n<pre><br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;div class=\\\"dt-links\\\"&gt;<br \\/> &lt;a href=\\\"#\\\"&gt;About&lt;\\/a&gt;<br \\/> | &lt;a href=\\\"#\\\"&gt;Data&lt;\\/a&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/>&lt;\\/div&gt;<\\/pre>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"styles-section-title styles-selector\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span>{\\/source}<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"17\",\"created\":\"2018-01-30 09:19:16\",\"created_by\":\"56\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-03-09 16:28:56\",\"modified_by\":\"56\",\"checked_out\":\"56\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-03-09 16:28:49\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-30 09:19:16\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\