ucing regions, effective climate change adaptation will determine the fates of billions of people. Effective adaptation requires knowing where increasingly scarce rains will fall, where snowpack will accumulate and melt, and where lack of precipitation of any kind will render specific locales uninhabitable.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In the coming years, the CHG will broaden its focus to include more nations, as well as longer time horizons.<\\/p>\\r\\n<pre><br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;div class=\\\"dt-links\\\"&gt;<br \\/> &lt;a href=\\\"#\\\"&gt;About&lt;\\/a&gt;<br \\/> | &lt;a href=\\\"#\\\"&gt;Data&lt;\\/a&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/> &lt;\\/div&gt;<br \\/>&lt;\\/div&gt;<\\/pre>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"styles-section-title styles-selector\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span>{\\/source}<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"21\",\"created\":\"2018-01-30 09:08:55\",\"created_by\":\"56\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-03-12 14:58:19\",\"modified_by\":\"56\",\"checked_out\":\"56\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-03-12 14:58:14\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-30 09:08:55\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"spfeatured_image\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"post_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"video\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"quote_text\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"quote_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"post_status\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"4\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(199,25,1,'','2018-03-14 12:32:04',56,6466,'926084228bc85aad8448b76f0dd0792bc9e8f2ec','{\"id\":25,\"asset_id\":\"112\",\"title\":\"Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u1ec1 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n\",\"alias\":\"gioi-thieu-ve-du-an\",\"introtext\":\"<p>{source}<span style=\\\"font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&lt;div class=\\\"bd-contentlayout-5 bd-sheetstyles-8 bd-no-margins bd-margins\\\"&gt;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">\\u00a0<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">D\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n Vietgeos (vi\\u1ebft t\\u1eaft c\\u1ee7a Vietnamese Geophysical Network) ra \\u0111\\u1eddi t\\u1eeb mong mu\\u1ed1n k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 khoa h\\u1ecdc c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00f3m c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u tr\\u1ebb c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111ang c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c \\u1edf n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u00e0i. V\\u1edbi m\\u1ea1ng l\\u01b0\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u v\\u1ec1 khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t \\u1edf Vi\\u1ec7t Nam v\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u00e0i \\u0111ang ng\\u00e0y m\\u1ed9t l\\u1edbn m\\u1ea1nh, vi\\u1ec7c k\\u00eat n\\u1ed1i c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 khoa h\\u1ecdc Vi\\u1ec7t Nam trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb kh\\u1eafp n\\u01a1i tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh m\\u1ed9t nhu c\\u1ea7u t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0m khoa h\\u1ecdc. \\u0110\\u00e2y s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch thi\\u1ebft th\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u00e2ng cao ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u v\\u00e0 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u00f3i chung cho Vi\\u1ec7t Nam. Do nhi\\u1ec1u y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t v\\u1ec1 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u, l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n t\\u00ednh to\\u00e1n c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf v\\u1eadt ch\\u1ea5t gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c n\\u01a1i tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi, vi\\u1ec7c k\\u00eat n\\u1ed1i c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 khoa h\\u1ecdc ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ec1 cho vi\\u1ec7c n\\u00e2ng cao ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng khoa h\\u1ecdc m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n cho ph\\u00e9p c\\u00e1c nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0m v\\u1ec1 khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t nam \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn nhanh nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c xu th\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 c\\u1eadp nh\\u1eadt trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c quan tr\\u1ecdng n\\u00e0y. C\\u00e1c chia s\\u1ebb h\\u1ecdc thu\\u1eadt, c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u, hay th\\u00f4ng tin h\\u1ecdc b\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea3o li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c c\\u1ee7a khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t nh\\u01b0 Kh\\u00ed T\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, Th\\u1ee7y V\\u0103n, H\\u1ea3i D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1ecdc, \\u0110\\u1ecba Ch\\u1ea5t, \\u0110\\u1ecba L\\u00fd, hay M\\u00f4i Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. C\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng tin chia s\\u1ebb ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mang t\\u00ednh t\\u1ef1 nguy\\u00ean v\\u00e0 phi l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn v\\u1edbi t\\u00f4n ch\\u1ec9 duy nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u v\\u1ec1 khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t trong v\\u00e0 ngo\\u00e0i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn Vi\\u1ec7t Nam. D\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n n\\u00e0y hi v\\u1ecdng s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t k\\u00eanh th\\u00f4ng tin t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap ng\\u00e0nh khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam ti\\u1ec7m c\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chu\\u1ea9n m\\u1ef1c v\\u00e0 xu th\\u1ebf m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi. M\\u1ecdi \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p chia s\\u1ebb th\\u00f4ng tin s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ghi nh\\u1eadn, v\\u1edbi mong mu\\u1ed1n t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean tham gia \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p cho trang k\\u1ebft n\\u00f4i n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd c\\u00f9ng h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ed9t m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch chung l\\u00e0 c\\u00f9ng nhau x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n ng\\u00e0nh khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u00eat Nam theo chu\\u1ea9n m\\u1ef1c khoa h\\u1ecdc qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 v\\u00e0 h\\u1eefu \\u00edch cho Vi\\u1ec7t Nam n\\u00f3i chung v\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0nh khoa h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u00f3i ri\\u00eang. <\\/span>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<pre><br \\/>&lt;\\/div&gt;<\\/pre>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"styles-section-title styles-selector\\\">{\\/source}<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"23\",\"created\":\"2018-01-30 09:06:48\",\"created_by\":\"56\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-03-14 12:32:04\",\"modified_by\":\"56\",\"checked_out\":\"56\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-03-14 12:31:42\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-30 09:06:48\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\